OL,3,CPolice close latest investigation into
OL,4,Cdisappearance of North Tyneside man
OL,6,FNorthumbria Police have announced the
OL,7,Flatest investigation into the historic
OL,8,Fdisappearance of a man from North
OL,9,FTyneside has been drawn to a close.
OL,11,FRobert Scott Clive went missing more
OL,12,Fthan 20 years ago, he was last seen
OL,13,Fshortly after 11pm on 10 October 2002
OL,14,Fin the Coronation Street area of North
OL,15,FShields.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
