PN,42402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774631480
OL,3,CPolice close latest investigation into
OL,4,Cdisappearance of North Tyneside man
OL,6,FThe then 30-year-old, who is
OL,7,Foriginally from Stranraer and is known
OL,8,Fas 'Scott', was reported missing by
OL,9,Fconcerned family members, and
OL,10,Ffollowing initial inquiries, police
OL,11,Flaunched a murder investigation.
OL,13,FUnconfirmed sightings in the early
OL,14,Fhours of the following day placed a
OL,15,Fman matching his description near the
OL,16,Fbanks of the River Tyne, although a
OL,17,Fbody was never found.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
