FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774631480
OL,3,CPolice close latest investigation into
OL,4,Cdisappearance of North Tyneside man
OL,6,FIn 2024, officers launched a new
OL,7,Finvestigation after further
OL,8,Finformation was shared about the
OL,9,Fevening Scott went missing.
OL,11,FAs part of the recent enquiries,
OL,12,Fsearches were carried out last year at
OL,13,Fan address in the Coronation Street
OL,14,Farea of North Shields ` a location
OL,15,FScott is known to have visited on the
OL,16,Fevening he went missing.
OL,18,FPolice said that as a result of new
OL,19,Finformation which came forward, there
OL,20,Fwas evidence to suggest Scott was
OL,21,Fassaulted on the night he went missing.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
