PN,42404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774631480
OL,3,CPolice close latest investigation into
OL,4,Cdisappearance of North Tyneside man
OL,6,FThree people ` two men aged in their
OL,7,F40s and 50s and one woman aged in her
OL,8,F40s ` were subsequently arrested on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,11,FThey were released on bail and have
OL,12,Fnow been told they will face no
OL,13,Ffurther action.
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Mark
OL,16,FAtherton, who led on the case, said:
OL,17,F"Our thoughts very much remain with
OL,18,FScott's family and I want to recognise
OL,19,Fthe strength they continue to show and
OL,20,Fthe support they have provided the
OL,21,Flatest investigation.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
