PN,42405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774631480
OL,3,CPolice close latest investigation into
OL,4,Cdisappearance of North Tyneside man
OL,6,F"We have exhausted all lines of
OL,7,Fenquiry currently available to us in
OL,8,Fan effort to try to provide them with
OL,9,Fthe answers they deserve.
OL,11,F"With no new leads and insufficient
OL,12,Fevidence to progress further, the
OL,13,Fdifficult decision has been made to
OL,14,Fdraw this current investigation to a
OL,15,Fclose.
OL,17,F"We remain open-minded about what
OL,18,Fhappened to Scott ` and should any new
OL,19,Finformation come forward, this will be
OL,20,Flooked into."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
