OL,3,CPolice close latest investigation into
OL,4,Cdisappearance of North Tyneside man
OL,6,FFollowing the conclusion of the
OL,7,Finvestigation, the family said: "We
OL,8,Fwould like to thank Northumbria Police
OL,9,Ffor all the effort they have put into
OL,10,Fthe investigation of the disappearance
OL,11,Fof our son Scott.
OL,13,F"We never got the final answer about
OL,14,FScott. But they have answered all our
OL,15,Fquestions and always kept us up to
OL,16,Fdate with the investigation.
OL,18,F"It's been a long 23 years ` and we
OL,19,Fstill hold hope for the final piece of
OL,20,Fthe jigsaw should the public have any
OL,21,Finformation."
OL,26,@oD@aOUuD@AOUzD@AOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
